data.title: Contemporary abstract art and education gifts
data.meta_description: Collagraph Printmaking Wax Specially formulated for creating on printing plates, ink and print as usual.  Endless possibilities to create your own collagraph prints on a full-size or mini-press.
data.text:
WAGNER ENCAUSTIC COLLAGRAPH WAX is a specially formulated encaustic white paint made for collagraph printing to easily release from the paper. Wagner Encaustic Collagraph White is used to build collagraph printing plates in lieu of collage materials. When inked, the texture of encaustic can be etched, scratched, carved, or embossed then inked and printed on an etching press to create monotypes on paper that are rich and full of depth. This product performs best using Akua non-toxic intaglio inks. The natural beeswax in Wagner Encaustic Collagraph White forms the perfect marriage with Akua soy and honey based intaglio inks.

Please refer to the video tutorial on getting started with Wagner Encaustic Collagraph White and refer to the Getting Started Guide.

ORDERS ARE HAND MADE BY ELISE WAGNER IN SMALL BATCHES

ALLOW 1 WEEK DOMESTIC AND 2 WEEKS INTERNATIONAL FOR DELIVERY.

FIRST-CLASS INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING AVAILABLE.
